
::SAGA DOCUMENTATION FILE::

:ADAPTOR NAME:

   Ssh Scp_File Adaptor


:AUTHORS:

  Copyright (c) 2011-2012 Andre Merzky <andre@merzky.net>


:LICENSE:

  Boost License 1.0


:ADAPTOR LIBRARY NAME:
  
   saga_adaptor_scp_file.so (dylib)


:IMPLEMENTS PACKAGE:
 
  - saga::filesystem


:DESCRIPTION:

  The adaptor provides means to manage and access remote files 
  via ssh, scp and sftp.


:URL SCHEMES:

  supported URL schemes are:

    any://
    ssh://
    scp://
    sftp://


:REQUIRES:

  In order to build and use the adaptor, the following components must be
  available:

  - ssh
  - scp
  - sftp



:CONFIGURE OPTIONS:



:INI FILE:

  saga_adaptor_scp_file.ini


:INI OPTIONS:

  none


:KNOWN ISSUES:

  Adaptor implementation is incomplete.
 
